# 🧠 1. SYSTEM OVERVIEW

## 🎯 Purpose

Build a backend system that:

* Collects BTC 15-minute market data from Polymarket
* Computes winning wallets
* Stores daily results
* Aggregates historical data
* Serves leaderboard via API

# 🏗️ High-Level Architecture

```text
Polymarket → Incremental Sync → Trades Table (Unique) → Hybrid API → Edge Cache → Frontend
```

